summary: I got legally married to my partner of 9 years
body:
I got legally married to my partner of 9 years

Granted, it’s not the actual wedding ceremony which will be in December, but still.

I can safely say Taylor’s music has played a role in my love life since I was a teen, and I’m so glad to say that I’m now at New Year’s Day and Call it what you want.

When David and I started dating about 9 years ago, I was in college and the song that stood out the most was “Mine” because we spent a lot of nights at the beach, sitting by the water, and it was beautiful. The memories were mine, and it was ours.

Thought I’d share since @taylorswift ’s songs played such a role in my life ♥️

“Hold on to the memories, they will hold on to you”
